Package: expectedevents
Title: Calculate the expected number of events
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Dominic", "Magirr", email = "d.magirr@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculate the expected number of events at data cut-off in time-to-event trials.
    Assumes piecewise exponential survival times, an (independent) exponential withdrawal rate,
    and recruitment following a simple power distribution.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.4)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    gsDesign,
    purrr,
    mvtnorm
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports: purrr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
